==Kumbharzuvem ganvant==
 
Hea ganvant dhennlo nachovpachi pod'dhot soman asli tori dhennleache ghumttek rothacho akar tantunt chandichi Krixnnachi murti bosovn , rothak guddeo laita ani Hanuman murti rothar bosovn dhennlo ghoraghoramni nachoit bhonvta.

Dhemnnlo bhonvtona protiek ghoran devak dil'leo poddi mhonnlear tandull, godd nal'l hi soglli samagri ekechkodden ekhttaita. Ekhttaim kel'li hi soglli samagri dongrar vhorun, thoim chul ghalun eka topan goddxem korun soglleank vantt'tat.Krixnnacho prosad mhonn khavpak dongrar lok mud'da' zomtat. Dongrar goddxem randpa fattlo hetu oso ki poili rakhnne gorvank choronvk dongrar vhortale thoinch te kidteim xizovn khatale teach karnnank lagun dongrar goddxem randhpachi pod'dhot.

Oso ho Goenchea vattharantlo gorvancho paddvo zo veg-veglleo riti-pod'dhotin monoitat.

